{"word":"H3213 - יָלַל - yâlal - yaw-lal' - Howl","slug":"H3213","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָלַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yâlal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-lal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Howl"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05DC;&#x05DC; - ya&#x0302;lal</b> - <i>yaw-lal'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>howl</i> (with a wailing tone) or <i>yell</i> (with a boisterous one): - (make to) howl, be howling."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3214\">H3214</a>, <a href=\"#/H3215\">H3215</a>"}]}